{"tid":2401668,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"原來以前去少幾次旅行，真係可以買到樓（仲要係full pay)","createTime":"2021-02-10T02:12:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-11T10:17:49.000Z","uid":36494,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"56bb3f6e5f01ed3f6dcace938c09c485f80d7842","tid":2401668,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T02:12:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GTitKjQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGTitKjQ.png&h=08ffcfcd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yqcm4jQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyqcm4jQ.png&h=fe2dea25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n60年代，出國旅遊仍然是奢侈享受，「去少啲日本」原來可以直接付首買樓上車！翻看舊報紙，1965年曾有旅行社登廣告，宣傳14天「堂皇日本遊」旅行團，遊歷的城市包括東京、名古屋、大阪、京都等等，飛機去、輪船返，回程更會停台灣，雙人房收費為每人2995元。而同年上車盤價格約為1.5萬元<span class=\"red\">，1人團費等同樓價兩成，2人同行團費則達樓價四成，而5人團費等於可買一個單位。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%86%B1%E7%88%86%E8%A9%B1%E9%A1%8C/251294/%E6%A8%93%E5%A5%B4-60%E5%B9%B4%E4%BB%A3%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%98%E8%B2%BB%E5%A4%A0%E7%95%80%E9%A6%96%E6%9C%9F-%E5%8E%BB%E5%B0%91%E5%B9%BE%E6%AC%A1%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E7%9C%9F%E4%BF%82%E8%B2%B7%E5%88%B0%E6%A8%93\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%2586%25B1%25E7%2588%2586%25E8%25A9%25B1%25E9%25A1%258C%2F251294%2F%25E6%25A8%2593%25E5%25A5%25B4-60%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC%25E5%259C%2598%25E8%25B2%25BB%25E5%25A4%25A0%25E7%2595%2580%25E9%25A6%2596%25E6%259C%259F-%25E5%258E%25BB%25E5%25B0%2591%25E5%25B9%25BE%25E6%25AC%25A1%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC%25E7%259C%259F%25E4%25BF%2582%25E8%25B2%25B7%25E5%2588%25B0%25E6%25A8%2593&d=%2BlEHcpGCWp7P1IX%2BOWqMQv4N63GW6AE6v5vQ0jPanwo%3D&h=f487e001\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%86%B1%E7%88%86%E8%A9%B1%E9%A1%8C/251294/%E6%A8%93%E5%A5%B4-60%E5%B9%B4%E4%BB%A3%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%98%E8%B2%BB%E5%A4%A0%E7%95%80%E9%A6%96%E6%9C%9F-%E5%8E%B